-{zh-cn:'''小查里斯·奧托·普斯''';zh-tw:'''CP查理'''，本名'''小查里斯·奧托·普斯'''}-（{{lang-en|Charles Otto Puth Jr.}}，{{bd|1991年|12月2日||}}），是一位美国[[歌手|歌手]]、詞曲作家及音樂製作人，出生于美国[[新泽西州|新泽西州]]{{link-en|拉姆森(新澤西州)|Rumson, New Jersey|拉姆森}}，在[[YouTube|YouTube]]上有很高的知名度。2015年，凭借与[[梅根·崔娜|梅根·崔娜]]合作的《[[马文·盖伊_(歌曲)|马文·盖]]》（''Marvin Gaye''）被大家所熟知，并迅速走红。之后，其与[[威茲·哈利法|威茲·哈利法]]合作演唱的《[[玩命關頭7|玩命關頭7]]》電影片尾曲《[[再见你一面|再见你一面]]》（''See You Again''）一举夺得美国[[告示牌百强单曲榜|告示牌百強單曲榜]]共計12週冠軍，并在[[澳大利亚|澳大利亚]]、[[奥地利|奥地利]]，[[英国|英国]]、[[德国|德国]]、[[加拿大|加拿大]]、[[新西兰|新西兰]]、[[爱尔兰|爱尔兰]]、[[瑞士|瑞士]]的单曲榜单排名第一，因此紅遍全球。2016年1月，與[[席琳娜·戈梅茲|席琳娜·戈梅茲]]合作的《[[不再甜蜜|不再甜蜜]]》（''We Don't Talk Anymore''）更突破他在[[YouTube|YouTube]]上以往的點擊率28億點擊率，成為查理·普斯第2首在告示牌百強單曲榜的前十單曲。2017年4月，查理·普斯釋出《[[Attention_(查理·普斯歌曲)|注意力]]》（''Attention ''），僅僅幾天便登上了[[告示牌百強單曲榜|告示牌百強單曲榜]]前十位。

== 早年生活 ==
查理·普斯生於1991年12月2日，在美國[[新澤西州|新澤西州]]{{link-en|拉姆森 (新澤西州)|Rumson, New Jersey|拉姆森}}長大。<ref name="jazz">{{cite news|title=Jazz Program Plays It Cool: At a Theater Named for Count Basie, Music Students Learn His Art Form|work=The Star-Ledger|location=Newark, New Jersey|date=2004-09-15|author=Allison Freeman|url=http://infoweb.newsbank.com/iw-search/we/InfoWeb?p_product=AWNB&p_theme=aggregated5&p_action=doc&p_docid=105221CE6570D51D&p_docnum=1&p_queryname=2|quote="Pianist Charlie Puth, 12, of Rumson, wants to be a professional musician. Charlie, who is working on recording his second CD, composes his own music. 'Jazz music is really cool and relaxing,' he said. 'I like doing all kinds of improvisation and stuff.'"|language=en}}</ref>父親查理·普斯是德國移民後裔，是一名天主教徒，<ref>{{cite news|author=Rob Copsey|url=http://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/charlie-puth-interview-it-took-years-to-become-an-overnight-success-__10335/|title=Charlie Puth interview: “It took years to become an overnight success”|website=Official Charts|date=2015-08-04|accessdate=2017-02-22|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170627214944/http://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/charlie-puth-interview-it-took-years-to-become-an-overnight-success-__10335/|archivedate=2017-06-27|deadurl=no}}</ref>从事地产中介工作。<ref name="家庭1">{{cite web|url=https://njmonthly.com/articles/jersey-living/people/charlie-puth-rumsons-pop-prodigy/|title=Charlie Puth, Rumson's Pop Prodigy|date=2016-01-12|language=en|accessdate=2017-02-22|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161008163517/https://njmonthly.com/articles/jersey-living/people/charlie-puth-rumsons-pop-prodigy/|archivedate=2016-10-08|deadurl=no}}</ref>母親黛布拉是[[猶太人|猶太人]]，<ref>{{cite web|author=Jessica Goodman|url=http://www.ew.com/article/2015/12/10/charlie-puth-golden-globe-grammys-nomination|title=Charlie Puth & Wiz Khalifa are going to look 'fly as f-' at the Grammys|website=EW.com|date=2015-12-10|accessdate=2017-02-22|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170710004207/http://ew.com/article/2015/12/10/charlie-puth-golden-globe-grammys-nomination/|archivedate=2017-07-10|deadurl=no}}</ref>从事音乐教师工作，<ref name="家庭1" /><ref name="家庭2">{{cite web|url=http://www.nj.com/entertainment/music/index.ssf/2016/01/charlie_puth_blossoms_into_njs_hottest_pop_star_th.html|title=How blossoming N.J. star Charlie Puth became pop's ascendant hit-maker|accessdate=2018-05-26|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180617122609/http://www.nj.com/entertainment/music/index.ssf/2016/01/charlie_puth_blossoms_into_njs_hottest_pop_star_th.html|archivedate=2018-06-17|deadurl=no}}</ref>并为HBO编写电视广告。<ref name="Independent-2016-01-29">{{cite news|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/music/charlie-puth-interview-being-bullied-for-pitch-perfect-talent-and-selena-gomezs-advice-on-dealing-a6841501.html|title=How Charlie Puth dealt with school bullies and the negative side of fame|author=Emily Jupp|date=2016-01-29|language=en|accessdate=2017-02-22|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161205113017/http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/music/charlie-puth-interview-being-bullied-for-pitch-perfect-talent-and-selena-gomezs-advice-on-dealing-a6841501.html|archivedate=2016-12-05|deadurl=no}}</ref>他有一个弟弟和一个妹妹，双胞胎史蒂芬和米凯拉，弟弟Stephen Puth也是位歌手。<ref name="家庭1" />

查理右邊的眉毛有道疤痕，據他自己在[[Twitter|Twitter]]所述，他幼時頭部嚴重受創，以致留下這疤痕。之後在一次雜誌訪問中，他透露這道疤痕是他在兩歲時被狗咬留下的。<ref>{{citation|url=http://www.christianitydaily.com/articles/3867/20150522/wiz-khalifa-s-see-you-again-singer-charlie-puth-on-why-his-eyebrow-is-shaved.htm|title=Wiz Khalifa's "See You Again" Singer Charlie Puth Talks Eyebrows: Why Is It Shaved?|3=|author=Gloria Lee|work=Christianity Daily|date=2015-05-22|accessdate=2017-02-23|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170121152146/http://www.christianitydaily.com/articles/3867/20150522/wiz-khalifa-s-see-you-again-singer-charlie-puth-on-why-his-eyebrow-is-shaved.htm|archivedate=2017-01-21|deadurl=no}}</ref>

查里拥有[[绝对音高|绝对音高]]，这是一种少有的音高感受能力。他能够在没有参考音高的情况下，辨别并唱出乐谱的实际音高。<ref name="家庭1" /><ref name="家庭2" /><ref name="Independent-2016-01-29" /><ref name="livingmedia-2015-01-06">{{cite news|url=http://www.livinginmedia.com/article/perfectly-pitched-for-success--charlie-puth.html|title=Perfectly Pitched For Success - Charlie Puth|author=Paul Williams|work=livinginmedia.com|date=2015-01-06|accessdate=2017-02-22|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170222200626/http://www.livinginmedia.com/article/perfectly-pitched-for-success--charlie-puth.html|archivedate=2017-02-22|deadurl=yes}}</ref>在他四岁时，他的母亲向他教授古典音乐和钢琴。<ref name="mtv-biography">{{cite web|url=http://www.mtv.com/artists/charlie-puth/biography/|title=Charlie Puth Bio {{!}} Charlie Puth Career|language=en|accessdate=2017-02-22|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170110220628/http://www.mtv.com/artists/charlie-puth/biography/|archivedate=2017-01-10|deadurl=no}}</ref>他在十岁时开始学习爵士乐，<ref name="mtv-biography" />并在十二岁时参加{{link-en|雷德班克|Red Bank, New Jersey}}贝西伯爵剧院的夏季青年爵士乐团。<ref name="jazz" /><ref name="家庭2" />之后，他被{{link-en|贝西伯爵剧院|Count Basie Theatre}}雇用，在[[查理·布朗|查理·布朗]]的制作中表演。<ref name="家庭2" />六年级时，他挨家挨户推销他自己录制并发行的圣诞专辑《Have a Merry Charlie Christmas》，卖得$600。<ref name="mtv-biography" /><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bostonglobe.com/arts/music/2015/08/03/berklee-honed-jersey-boy-charlie-puth-heads-top/JWw202vGUJ9Z8qedgOpLHO/story.html|title=Berklee-honed Jersey boy Charlie Puth heads to the top - The Boston Globe|3=|author=James Sullivan|date=2015-08-03|language=en|accessdate=2017-08-28|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170828183552/https://www.bostonglobe.com/arts/music/2015/08/03/berklee-honed-jersey-boy-charlie-puth-heads-top/JWw202vGUJ9Z8qedgOpLHO/story.html|archivedate=2017-08-28|deadurl=no}}</ref>

他于{{link-en|拉姆森 (新澤西州)|Rumson, New Jersey|拉姆森}}圣十字学院和{{link-en|福雷斯特戴尔中学|Rumson School District#Schools}}就读，<ref name="livingmedia-2015-01-06" />并于2010年在{{link-en|拉姆森费尔纽黑文地区高中|Rumson-Fair Haven Regional High School}}畢業<ref>{{Cite web|author=Chris Jordan|url=http://www.app.com/story/entertainment/music/2015/07/19/charlie-puth-jersey-shores-newest-star/30393915/|title=Charlie Puth is the Jersey Shore’s newest star|publisher={{link-en|Asbury Park Press|Asbury Park Press}}|date=2015-07-19|quote=Charlie Puth of Rumson is on the phone from Los Angeles.... He’s an overnight success. The thing is, of course, it didn’t happen overnight. Puth went to Rumson-Fair Haven High School, but he didn’t play local clubs or coffeehouses.|accessdate=2017-02-22|language=en}}</ref>。七年级时，他于[[曼哈顿音乐学院|曼哈顿音乐学院]]<ref name="成名">{{cite news|title=Berklee Student a YouTube Star|work=Boston Herald|date=2012-09-09|author=Robert Koehler|url=http://infoweb.newsbank.com/iw-search/we/InfoWeb?p_product=AWNB&p_theme=aggregated5&p_action=doc&p_docid=141395B2356D3F00&p_docnum=2&p_queryname=10|language=en}}</ref>学习预科课程，主修爵士钢琴，兼修古典音乐。<ref name="livingmedia-2015-01-06" /><ref>{{cite web|url=http://network.online.berklee.edu/members/40959|title=Charlie Puth {{!}} Berklee Music Network|author=Berklee College of Music|website=network.online.berklee.edu|language=en|accessdate=2016-08-21|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160829002748/http://network.online.berklee.edu/members/40959|archivedate=2016-08-29|deadurl=no}}</ref>之後獲全額獎學金，入讀[[伯克利音樂學院|伯克利音樂學院]]，主修音樂製作及工程<ref>{{Cite web|title=Charlie Puth / Taylor Berrett {{!}} Berklee College of Music events|url=https://www.berklee.edu/events/charlie-puth-taylor-berrett|website=www.berklee.edu|accessdate=2015-08-10|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151005161617/https://www.berklee.edu/events/charlie-puth-taylor-berrett|archivedate=2015-10-05|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。

== 演艺生涯 ==
=== 2009－2014年：事业开端 ===
2009年9月，查理·普斯建立自己的[[Youtube|Youtube]]频道，命名为“Charlies Vlogs”，并在频道中上傳短剧以及翻唱歌曲。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nj.com/entertainment/music/index.ssf/2015/04/how_an_nj_singers_simple_hook_became_the_no_1_song.html#incart_river|title=How a N.J. singer's simple hook became the No. 1 song in the world|author=Bobby Olivier|date=2015-04-23|accessdate=2017-02-27|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170619131612/http://www.nj.com/entertainment/music/index.ssf/2015/04/how_an_nj_singers_simple_hook_became_the_no_1_song.html#incart_river|archivedate=2017-06-19|deadurl=no}}</ref>2010年，查理發布他第一首歌曲《These Are My Sexy Shades》的音乐录影带。<ref>{{Cite AV media|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ClgV1jBB9ME|title=These Are My Sexy Shades - Charlie Puth|accessdate=2015-12-11|publisher=Youtube|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180719153414/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ClgV1jBB9ME|archivedate=2018-07-19|deadurl=no}}</ref>12月10日，他独立发行首张迷你专辑《The Otto Tunes》。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://play.spotify.com/album/43TkICa0ghoWf1UFECLCpx|title=The Otto Tunes by Charlie Puth - EP|work=Spotify|accessdate=2015-12-11}}</ref>2011年，他与艾米莉·卢瑟演唱[[阿黛尔|阿黛尔]]的《Someone like You》赢得由[[佩雷斯·希尔顿|佩雷斯·希尔顿]]赞助的線上比赛《Can You Sing?》。<ref name="成名" />同年，[[艾伦·德杰尼勒斯|艾伦·德杰尼勒斯]]表示，在看过他们演唱的《Someone like You》后，她与查理和艾米莉签约加入她的唱片公司{{link-en|eleveneleven|eleveneleven}}。<ref>{{cite news|title=Emily Luther Scores Recording Contract - From Ellen|work=The Valley Breeze|location=Cumberland, Rhode Island|date=2011-10-13|author=Frank O'Donnell|url=http://infoweb.newsbank.com/iw-search/we/InfoWeb?p_product=AWNB&p_theme=aggregated5&p_action=doc&p_docid=13A5BB24D80AF3F8&p_docnum=1&p_queryname=6}}</ref>查理在演出中演唱这首歌曲。<ref>{{cite news|title=Woonsocket Woman to Sing Wednesday on 'Ellen'|work=Providence Journal|location=Providence, Rhode Island|date=2011-10-04|url=http://infoweb.newsbank.com/iw-search/we/InfoWeb?p_product=AWNB&p_theme=aggregated5&p_action=doc&p_docid=152422A90DF39050&p_docnum=6&p_queryname=7}}</ref>2012年12月，查理發行了一首宣传单曲《Break Again》，艾米莉·卢瑟参与了演唱。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://play.spotify.com/track/1s4MBNagYqVmZT9CD2STbn?play=true&utm_source=open.spotify.com&utm_medium=open|title=Break Again|work=Spotify|accessdate=2015-12-11}}</ref>音乐录影带在数天后发表。<ref>{{Cite AV media|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rnFNpP0MJyE|title=Break Again - Charlie Puth & Emily Luther (Official Music Video)|accessdate=2017-02-27|publisher=[[Youtube|Youtube]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170916114848/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rnFNpP0MJyE|archivedate=2017-09-16|deadurl=no}}</ref>2012年1月25日，查理和艾米莉在[[艾伦·德杰尼勒斯秀|艾伦·德杰尼勒斯秀]]中共同演唱这首歌曲以及[[怀旧女郎|怀旧女郎]]的《{{link-en|Need You Now|Need You Now (Lady Antebellum song)}}》。<ref>{{cite news|title=Talk Shows|work=The Fresno Bee|location=Fresno, California|date=2012-01-25|url=http://infoweb.newsbank.com/iw-search/we/InfoWeb?p_product=AWNB&p_theme=aggregated5&p_action=doc&p_docid=13C836C4FA132830&p_docnum=6&p_queryname=10}}</ref>2012年10月，查理在活动中为世界最大的[[骨髓|骨髓]]捐献中心DKMS演出。<ref>{{cite news|title=NY Knick Tyson Chandler Gets Cheek Swabbed To Delete Blood Cancer: Joins Supermodel Jessica White, Bally Creative Directors, DKMS Delete Blood Cancer Co-Founder Katharina Harf To Launch Lips For Life Collection|publisher=PR Newswire|date=2012-10-26|work=DKMS Delete Blood Cancer |format=press release|url=http://infoweb.newsbank.com/iw-search/we/InfoWeb?p_product=AWNB&p_theme=aggregated5&p_action=doc&p_docid=1422BCE96A8ABB58&p_docnum=1&p_queryname=10}}</ref>2012年后期，查理离开eleveneleven。

2013年10月23日，查理在[[流媒体|流媒体]]发行第二张独立迷你专辑《Ego》。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://open.spotify.com/album/3tK1UC5h0T1pG4MPV3z8P5|title=Ego by Charlie Puth - EP|work=Spotify|accessdate=2015-12-11|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304201311/https://open.spotify.com/album/3tK1UC5h0T1pG4MPV3z8P5|archivedate=2016-03-04|deadurl=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.discogs.com/Charlie-Puth-Ego/release/7993528|title=Ego - Charlie Puth|work=Discogs|accessdate=2017-02-27|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170814222337/https://www.discogs.com/Charlie-Puth-Ego/release/7993528|archivedate=2017-08-14|deadurl=no}}</ref>他参与许多{{link-en|Youtube制作者|List of YouTubers}}的歌曲、音乐创作以及专辑制作。他创作了[[谢恩·多森|谢恩·多森]]的[[播客|播客]]《Shane and Friends》的主题曲、[[夏恩·卡尔|夏恩·卡尔]]视频博客的片头曲、《{{link-en|Internet Killed Televison|Internet Killed Televison}}》的主题曲、一首Youtube组合Our 2nd Life巡回演唱会和电影的歌曲以及Our 2nd Life成员{{link-en|瑞奇·狄龙|Ricky Dillon}}的数首单曲。2014年，他发行宣传单曲《L.U.V》。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://play.spotify.com/album/6Zglv4NjUqzoW8xU9zEVlQ|title=L.U.V. - Charlie Puth|work=Spotify|accessdate=2015-12-11|archive-date=2021-02-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210213034650/https://open.spotify.com/album/6Zglv4NjUqzoW8xU9zEVlQ|dead-url=no}}</ref>音乐录影带由安德鲁·瓦伦丁担任导演。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.andrewvallentine.com/#/luv-1/|title=L.U.V. (2014) by Charlie Puth|work=Andrew Vallentine Official|accessdate=2017-02-27|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170228082421/http://www.andrewvallentine.com/#/luv-1/|archivedate=2017-02-28|deadurl=no}}</ref>同年，在[[皮普保罗|皮普保罗]]的第八张录音室专辑《{{link-en|Globalization|Globalization (album)}}》中，他共同创作歌曲《Celebrate》。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.allmusic.com/song/celebrate-mt0050953845|title=Pitbull - Celebrate (From The Original Motion Picture Penguins Of Madagascar)|publisher=Allmusic|accessdate=2015-05-03|date=2014-11-17|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160309102411/http://www.allmusic.com/song/celebrate-mt0050953845|archivedate=2016-03-09|deadurl=no}}</ref>

=== 2015年至今：《天马行空》 ===
[[File:Spectacle_Charlie_Puth_dans_la_festival_des_montgolfières_2015_au_St-Jean-Sur-Richelieu.jpg|thumb]]
2015年初，查理·普斯与[[大西洋唱片|大西洋唱片]]签约，过往作品从[[iTunes|iTunes]]中移除。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://next2shine.com/atlantic-records-signs-next-youtube-star-charlie-puth|title=Atlantic Records signs the next YouTube star, Charlie Puth - "Marvin Gaye" Single with Meghan Trainor|author=Candice M|work=Next2Shine|date=2015-01-19|accessdate=2017-03-11|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170628171109/http://next2shine.com/atlantic-records-signs-next-youtube-star-charlie-puth|archivedate=2017-06-28|deadurl=no}}</ref>2015年2月，查理發行了独立单曲《{{link-en|马文盖伊|Marvin Gaye (song)}}》，由[[梅根·崔娜|梅根·崔娜]]伴唱。<ref name="瑞士">{{cite web|url=http://swisscharts.com/showinterpret.asp?interpret=Charlie+Puth|title=Discographie Charlie Puth|publisher=Swiss Charts Portal. Hung Medien (Steffen Hung)|accessdate=2017-03-11|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303231323/http://swisscharts.com/showinterpret.asp?interpret=Charlie+Puth|archivedate=2016-03-03|deadurl=no}}</ref>单曲在澳大利亚的销量认证为2× 白金，在新西兰、爱尔兰和英国位居榜首，在美国[[公告牌百强单曲榜|公告牌百强单曲榜]]最高排名为21。<ref name="新西兰">{{cite web|url=http://charts.org.nz/showinterpret.asp?interpret=Charlie+Puth|title=Discography Charlie Puth|publisher=New Zealand Charts Portal. Hung Medien (Steffen Hung)|accessdate=2017-03-11|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160210080250/http://charts.org.nz/showinterpret.asp?interpret=Charlie+Puth|archivedate=2016-02-10|deadurl=no}}</ref><ref name="英国">{{cite web|url=http://www.officialcharts.com/artist/48109/charlie-puth/|title=Charlie Puth|publisher=[[Official_Charts_Company|Official Charts Company]]|work=Officialcharts.com|accessdate=2017-03-11|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161114141224/http://www.officialcharts.com/artist/48109/charlie-puth/|archivedate=2016-11-14|deadurl=no}}</ref>查理创作、共同制作并与[[维兹·卡利法|维兹·卡利法]]共同演唱了《[[再见你一面|再见你一面]]》。歌曲是对[[保罗·沃克|保罗·沃克]]的悼念，收录于《[[玩命關頭7_(原聲帶)|速度与激情7：电影原声带]]》。卡利法创作了说唱歌词，剩余部分由查理创作。歌曲于公告牌百强单曲榜非连续12周登顶。<ref name="公告牌100">{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/artist/6473237/charlie+puth/chart?f=379|title=Charlie Puth – Chart History: Hot 100|work=[[告示牌_(雜誌)|Billboard]]|accessdate=2017-03-11|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160813031634/http://www.billboard.com/artist/6473237/Charlie+Puth/chart?f=379|archivedate=2016-08-13|deadurl=no}}</ref><ref name="澳大利亚">{{cite web|url=http://australian-charts.com/showinterpret.asp?interpret=Charlie+Puth|title=Discography Charlie Puth|publisher=Australian Charts Portal. Hung Medien (Steffen Hung)|accessdate=2017-03-11|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160407055150/http://www.australian-charts.com/showinterpret.asp?interpret=Charlie+Puth|archivedate=2016-04-07|deadurl=no}}</ref>《再见你一面》获得三项[[格莱美奖|格莱美奖]]提名：年度歌曲、最佳流行组合或合唱团和最佳影视媒体作品歌曲。歌曲还入围{{link-en|BBC音乐奖|BBC Music Awards}}年度歌曲并获得[[第73届金球奖|第73届金球奖]][[金球奖最佳原创歌曲|最佳原创歌曲]]提名。<ref>{{cite news|author1=Stephanie Merry|author2=Emily Yahr|title=Golden Globes nominations 2016: Complete list|url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/arts-and-entertainment/wp/2015/12/10/golden-globes-nominations-2016-complete-coverage/|accessdate=2017-03-11|work=[[华盛顿邮报|The Washington Post]]|date=2015-12-10|language=en|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108105815/https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/arts-and-entertainment/wp/2015/12/10/golden-globes-nominations-2016-complete-coverage/|dead-url=no}}</ref>查理为[[崔·颂|崔·颂]]制作歌曲《{{link-en|Slow Motion|Slow Motion (Trey Songz song)}}》，并安排了与[[李尔·韦恩|李尔·韦恩]]和[[杰森·德鲁罗|杰森·德鲁罗]]的共同演唱。<ref>{{cite web|title=Video: Trey Songz – ‘Slow Motion’|date=2015-02-14|accessdate=2017-03-11|url=http://www.rap-up.com/2015/02/14/video-trey-songz-slow-motion/|website={{link-en|Rap-Up|Rap-Up}}|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171012044807/http://www.rap-up.com/2015/02/14/video-trey-songz-slow-motion/|archivedate=2017-10-12|deadurl=no}}</ref>

查理于音乐录影带《{{link-en|Dear Future Husband|Dear Future Husband}}》中饰演[[梅根·崔娜|梅根·崔娜]]的心仪对象。她于{{link-en|在线约会服务|online dating service}}中结识查理，查理带着[[比萨饼|比萨饼]]外卖来到崔娜的家，成功给崔娜留下印象。录影带结尾，崔娜微笑着邀请查理进入她的家。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.vevo.com/watch/meghan-trainor/dear-future-husband/USSM21500380|title=Meghan Trainor - Dear Future Husband|publisher=[[Vevo|Vevo]]|accessdate=2017-03-11|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170207194846/http://www.vevo.com/watch/meghan-trainor/dear-future-husband/USSM21500380|archivedate=2017-02-07|deadurl=no}}</ref>2015年5月1日，查理發行了包含五首歌曲的迷你专辑《{{link-en|Some Type of Love|Some Type of Love}}》。<ref name="公告牌-2015-03-17">{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/6502317/charlie-puth-tonight-show-interview|title=Charlie Puth Talks Meghan Trainor Duet 'Marvin Gaye' & His Plea to James Taylor|author=Trevor Anderson|work=Billboard|date=2015-03-17|accessdate=2017-03-11|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170313200555/http://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/pop-shop/6502317/charlie-puth-tonight-show-interview|archivedate=2017-03-13|deadurl=no}}</ref>2015年6月，他与[[李尔·韦恩|李尔·韦恩]]发行了宣传单曲《{{link-en|Nothing but Trouble|Nothing but Trouble (song)}}》，歌曲来自纪录片《808: The Movie》的原声带。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rap-up.com/2015/06/29/new-music-lil-wayne-charlie-puth-nothing-but-trouble/|title=New Music: Lil Wayne & Charlie Puth - "Nothing But Trouble"|work={{link-en|Rap-Up|Rap-Up}}|date=2015-06-29|accessdate=2017-03-11|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170731120852/http://www.rap-up.com/2015/06/29/new-music-lil-wayne-charlie-puth-nothing-but-trouble/|archivedate=2017-07-31|deadurl=no}}</ref>2015年期间，查理参与制作数张其他歌手的专辑。他共同创作、制作[[杰森·德鲁罗|杰森·德鲁罗]]专辑《{{link-en|Everything Is 4|Everything Is 4}}》中的《Broke》和《Pull Up》，<ref name="德鲁罗-Everything Is 4">{{cite web|url=http://www.allmusic.com/album/everything-is-4-mw0002841735|title=Everything Is 4|publisher=Allmusic|accessdate=2015-05-03|date=2014-11-17|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150711142533/http://www.allmusic.com/album/everything-is-4-mw0002841735|archivedate=2015-07-11|deadurl=no}}</ref>共同创作[[邦尼·麦琪|邦尼·麦琪]]专辑《{{link-en|Bombastic|Bombastic (Bonnie McKee EP)}}》中的同名歌曲，<ref>{{cite web|url=https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/bombastic-clean-single/id997560619|title=iTunes - Music - Bombastic (Clean) - Single by Bonnie McKee|website=[[iTunes_Store|iTunes Store]] US|publisher=[[苹果公司|Apple Inc.]]|accessdate=2017-03-11|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150528014152/https://itunes.apple.com/us/album/bombastic-clean-single/id997560619|archivedate=2015-05-28|deadurl=no}}</ref>并制作{{link-en|席洛·格林|CeeLo Green}}专辑《{{link-en|Heart Blanche|Heart Blanche}}》中的《Working Class Heroes》。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.allmusic.com/album/heart-blanche-mw0002883401|title=Heart Blanche|publisher=Allmusic|accessdate=2015-05-27|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151015010821/http://www.allmusic.com/album/heart-blanche-mw0002883401|archivedate=2015-10-15|deadurl=no}}</ref>

查理首张独立录音室专辑《[[天馬行空_(CP查理專輯)|天马行空]]》以及第二首单曲《{{link-en|爱在咫尺|One Call Away (Charlie Puth song)}}》的预购于2015年8月20日开始。歌曲在美国的最高排名为12，在英国的最高排名为26，并于澳大利亚取得第4名的成绩。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.officialcharts.com/search/singles/one%20call%20away/|title=Chart history - One Call Away|work=[[Official_Charts_Company|Official Charts Company]]|accessdate=2017-03-11|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161204075027/http://www.officialcharts.com/search/singles/one%20call%20away/|archivedate=2016-12-04|deadurl=no}}</ref>截至2016年2月，歌曲在美国国内的销量为513700。<ref name="美国销量">{{cite web|url=http://headlineplanet.com/home/2016/02/01/charlie-puths-one-call-away-crosses-the-500k-us-sales-mark/|title=Charlie Puth's "One Call Away" crosses 500K US sales mark|author=Brian Cantor|work=Headline Planet|date=2016-02-01|accessdate=2017-03-11|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170204160143/http://headlineplanet.com/home/2016/02/01/charlie-puths-one-call-away-crosses-the-500k-us-sales-mark/|archivedate=2017-02-04|deadurl=no}}</ref>查理發行了这首歌曲的重混，命名为《爱在咫尺 (Coast to Coast Mix)》，由美国说唱歌手[[Tyga|Tyga]]、{{link-en|Ty Dolla Sign|Ty Dolla Sign}}、乡村音乐录音歌手{{link-en|布雷特·埃尔德雷奇|Brett Eldredge}}以及墨西哥歌手{{link-en|索菲娅·雷耶斯|Sofia Reyes}}伴唱。<ref>{{Cite AV media|author1=Charlie Puth|author2={{link-en|Brett Eldredge|Brett Eldredge}}|author3={{link-en|Ty Dolla $ign|Ty Dolla Sign}}|author4=[[Tyga|Tyga]]|author5={{link-en|Sofia Reyes|Sofia Reyes}}|date=2015-11-22|title=One Call Away [Coast To Coast Mix] - Charlie Puth, Brett Eldredge, Ty Dolla $ign & Sofia Reyes|accessdate=2017-03-11|language=en|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OFZBMPg2y3w|publisher=[[Youtube|Youtube]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151127053650/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OFZBMPg2y3w|archivedate=2015-11-27|deadurl=no}}</ref>

他的独立专辑《[[天馬行空_(CP查理專輯)|天马行空]]》于2016年1月29日发行。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.amazon.co.uk/Nine-Track-Mind-Charlie-Puth/dp/B014Q29AO4/ref=sr_1_30_twi_aud_1?s=music&ie=UTF8&qid=1451500393&sr=1-30&keywords=charlie+puth|title=Nine Track Mind by Charlie Puth: Amazon.co.uk: Music|accessdate=2017-03-11|work=Amazon.co.uk|language=en}}</ref>专辑以第三名登陆英国排行榜，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/sia-s-this-is-acting-makes-a-play-for-official-albums-chart-top-spot__13691/|title=Sia’s This Is Acting makes a play for Official Albums Chart top spot|author=Rob Copsey|publisher=[[Official_Charts_Company|Official Charts Company]]|date=2016-02-01|accessdate=2017-03-11|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160204065516/http://www.officialcharts.com/chart-news/sia-s-this-is-acting-makes-a-play-for-official-albums-chart-top-spot__13691/|archivedate=2016-02-04|deadurl=no}}</ref>在[[公告牌二百强专辑榜|公告牌二百强专辑榜]]的最高排名为第六名。
2016年3月，查理开始了他的独立演唱会，天马行空巡回演唱会。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.charlieputh.com/tour|title=Nine Track Mind Tour|accessdate=2017-03-11|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170512034541/http://www.charlieputh.com/tour|archivedate=2017-05-12|deadurl=no}}</ref>

2016年，查理成为第一位与德意志音乐签约的歌手。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://adage.com/article/agency-news/deutschmusic-signs-grammy-nominated-pop-singer-charlie-puth/302191/|title=Deutsch Music Signs Grammy Nominated Pop Singer Charlie Puth|author=Lindsay Stein|date=2016-01-20|accessdate=2017-03-11|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161201141909/http://adage.com/article/agency-news/deutschmusic-signs-grammy-nominated-pop-singer-charlie-puth/302191/|archivedate=2016-12-01|deadurl=no}}</ref> 同年8月，查理首度赴台開唱。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://memeon-music.com/2016/08/16/charlie-puth/|title=【玩命關頭7】冠軍神曲〈See You Again〉主唱CP查理 榮獲白金唱片 珍珠奶茶一吸上癮|accessdate=2018-07-06|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180706194232/https://memeon-music.com/2016/08/16/charlie-puth/|archivedate=2018-07-06|deadurl=no}}</ref>

